Gujral E-Sales Power BI Dashboard
This interactive Power BI dashboard is designed to provide a clear, data-driven overview of e-sales performance using the right set of KPIs such as Total Sales, Profit, and Growth. 
It features cards for high-level metrics, enabling quick snapshots of performance.
The dashboard incorporates time-series analysis to track trends over months and weekdays, helping identify peak sales periods. 
Slicers and filters are added to allow users to drill down by state and quarter, enhancing interactivity and personalization. 
A consistent color theme has been applied throughout to ensure a visually cohesive and professional appearance.
This solution supports strategic decision-making by highlighting top-performing products, underperforming categories, and regional disparities in revenue.
